  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下物流系统的核心模块关系。首先，TrackingNumber作为审计入口，应该能追溯到Warehouse的定义层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Audit指向Define。那FleetManagement和StockLevel之间是什么关系？看起来是双向的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，FleetManagement和StockLevel是互相依赖的。车队调度需要实时库存数据，库存预警也要反馈给车队调整运力。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，双向箭头已加上。Warehouse这块我注意到有两个节点，Code和Define，需要区分一下吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Code是Warehouse的编码实现层，Define是定义层，Code应该指向Define。另外Define还要直接关联StockLevel做库存定义。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成，Code→Define→Barg的链路已建立。Risk和Signal这两个节点是做什么的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Risk是风险监控节点，它触发Signal信号，然后Signal再传递给StockLevel进行库存风险干预。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Risk→Signal→Barg，这个链路清楚了。Place和Press呢？看起来Place是孤立的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Place是仓位管理，Press是压力测试触发，Place通过Press动作来验证仓位承载能力。不过这里Press不需要指向其他模块，它是触发式的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，Place—Press用无向连接表示触发关系。我检查一下整体：Audit→Define，Bail↔Barg，还有遗漏吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，FleetManagement也要直接连到StockLevel，我之前说的双向是对的，但Bail→Barg的方向我确认一下——应该是Bail指向Barg，同时Barg也指向Bail，你画的是双向箭头吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认是双向的，Bail↔Barg。现在所有节点都连通了：TrackingNumber审计入口、Warehouse双层结构、风险信号链路、车队库存双向依赖，还有仓位压力测试。结构完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
